  "Two identical circles": "",
  "One circle inside the other": "",
  "Two non-overlapping circles with no intersection": "",
  "Mutually exclusive events have no overlap: P(A ∩ B) = 0. The circles are separate.": "",
  "Using a Venn diagram, if P(A) = 0.7, P(B) = 0.5, and P(A ∩ B) = 0.3, what is P(A only), i.e., P(A but not B)?": "",
  "0.3": "",
  "0.4": "",
  "P(A only) = P(A) − P(A ∩ B) = 0.7 − 0.3 = 0.4.": "",
